							<h3 class="lg:text-2xl lg:mb-5 lg:pb-5 text-lg mb-3 pb-3 font-semibold relative after:w-full after:h-px after:absolute after:opacity-30 after:left-0 after:bottom-0 after:bg-linear-(--title2-gradient) [.box-hover.active_&]:after:bg-linear-(--title3-gradient) [.box-hover.active_&]:text-white">Bilimsel Yaklaşım</h3>
